Quote: [caption] The humble snarler is increasingly taking on airs. .. SNARLER This synonym for sausage is unique to this country. Its origin is obscure, but Harry Orsman in his <i>Dictionary of Modern New Zealand Slang</i> theorises that it is "a play on the fancy that stray [snarly] dogs are used in their manufacture."
